            <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en"><p><supplied reason="subaudible">Tomb</supplied> of M(arkos) Aur(elios) <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign xml:lang="la">M(arcus) Aurelius</foreign></supplied> Betia: thus the spirit decided [ . . .</p></div>
